OL,3,CJersey politician says Bailiff
OL,4,Creferendum is 'under consideration'
OL,6,FA Jersey politician has suggested that
OL,7,Fa public referendum could allow
OL,8,Fislanders to have their say on the
OL,9,Fisland's Bailiff role.
OL,11,FIt comes as Connetable Andy Jehan
OL,12,Flodged a proposition to remove the
OL,13,FBailiff from Jersey's States Assembly.
OL,15,FHowever, former Bailiff, Deputy Philip
OL,16,FBailhache, has suggested that a public
OL,17,Freferendum should be brought forward
OL,18,Fto allow residents to voice their
OL,19,Fdecision.
