OL,3,CJersey politician says Bailiff
OL,4,Creferendum is 'under consideration'
OL,6,FCurrently, the Bailiff is a crown-
OL,7,Fappointed role responsible for the
OL,8,FStates Assembly's orderly conduct.
OL,10,FSimilar to the UK's Speaker of the
OL,11,FHouse, Sir Lindsay Hoyle, the Bailiff
OL,12,Fpresides over States proceedings, but
OL,13,Fcannot vote.
OL,15,FDeputy Andy Jehan has called
OL,16,Fpreviously for the States Assembly to
OL,17,Fbe able to select its own Speaker and
OL,18,FDeputy Speaker.
